* Add Comments\nto Tables & Columns
** COMMENT ON
***_ Add to tables, columns, schemas
***_ Markdown formatting supported
** CREATE TABLE
***_ Inline COMMENT on column definition
** ALTER TABLE
***_ ALTER COLUMN ... COMMENT
** AI-generated
***_ Catalog Explorer → AI generate
***_ Review before accepting
***_ Not for PII classification
** Required permissions
***_ Ownership OR MODIFY + SELECT
***_ USE CATALOG + USE SCHEMA
